English:
Hello OpenSteam users, I wanted to thank the few but diverse people who use this program, which has caused me so many headaches ;).
I wanted to announce that I'm working on an OpenSteamCLI, which functions practically the same as the current OpenSteam, but through a terminal. This will allow you to patch and install games without needing to download OpenSteam :D.
I'm doing this for people who are afraid to download third-party programs but want to try this blessing. I'll keep you updated on my Twitter @Robot22221 (TheJbrequi)

